data.description: Discover this captivating property spanning 13.77 acres, that offers a seamless blend of traditional charm and modern convenience. With 4 to 5 spacious bedrooms, including a second-floor primary bedroom with a sitting area, a welcoming living room, and an inviting dining room, the home provides ample space for comfortable living. The property features a barn, cross-fenced sections, and a guest house, opening doors to various uses such as cattle ranching, equestrian activities, and hunting. The cleared acreage enjoys road frontage along FM 92 S, ensuring easy accessibility while preserving its idyllic setting. This home exudes warmth with a wood-burning fireplace and offers year-round comfort through central electric cooling and heating systems. Embrace the rare chance to own a slice of Tyler County paradise and explore the potential of country living on expansive acreage. Schedule your showing today!
